professional sanga kura garda, instant chat ta hudaina, booking garnu parxa. will have to use the calender api and meet api for starting the meet.



Professional → Login → Google OAuth → Store tokens → Mark them as verified

User → chooses professional → frontend calls backend:
    backend → getBusySlots()
    backend → generate free slots
    return to frontend

User → selects a free slot → click Book

Backend → events.insert → add event to professional’s Google Calendar
Backend → send confirmation to user
